textBeforeTable: [edit] applications Docbooks of these modules can be found in module name/doc/program name of the KDE Git but the location is unsystematic so you should inspect the whole tree to find the correct item (there are many duplicates with KDE 4 counterparts). [edit] KDE Frameworks Please feel free to add your comments or suggestions to this table. If you want to update a docbook and do not know where to begin, subscribe to kde-doc-english АТ kde.org and ask your questions.
